{"tid":642252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與5青年推撞爭執　阿叔被圍毆倒地","createTime":"2018-04-25T15:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T15:45:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b09ab22442de2d8a0067d3631f8f39548ceafe0e","tid":642252,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180425/20372600?_ga=2.49391270.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20372600%3F_ga%3D2.49391270.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=uCLBvvLhmdvOTtrxMbsb3zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=98fe65f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F20372600%3F_ga%3D2.49391270.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=bbe70748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180425/20372600?_ga=2.49391270.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月25日 <br />\n<br />\n與5青年推撞爭執　阿叔被圍毆倒地<br />\n<br />\n4,846<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】彩虹邨前晚10時許上演街頭擂台。居民萬先生在家中突然聽到樓下嘈吵聲，探頭出窗即見金華樓對開的7-11便利店，有多人圍毆一名男子；他於是拍下經過。<br />\n<br />\n片段所見，一名穿黑衣牛仔褲的男子，與對方最少5名青年因身體碰撞問題發生爭執，其間雙方大打出手，更由便利店內打至店外。男事主寡不敵眾，被眾男推埋牆柱，遭對方箍頸推倒地上，對方多人隨即對他拳打腳踢，狂揼其臉部，最後有人再腳踢他臉部一下，事主隨即攤軟地上，再無反抗掙扎，有兇徒走向他望一望，見他仍有反應，眾人始悻悻然離去。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕到，將姓李（51歲）事主送往聯合醫院院治理，他鼻及口部受傷，警員在附近兜截疑人，惜未有發現。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n運署擬斥兩億　裝車牌識別系統<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n膠鞋累男童被夾扶手梯　消防溫柔安慰"},{"pid":"74fbb1dccbaa1eb9d7cf40ee0c53041622e22cd6","tid":642252,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母邊撚個省我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f687068bb9e8cdb45049dfd0169f8555db97d0b","tid":642252,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:37:21.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/25/233721_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F233721_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=fc3b67f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87dffa82c503a0f490965f9cdd277ece29b3705c","tid":642252,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"196ee679d5740addabedb72a2d35d333d8dd5d27","tid":642252,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2a3749dad89ca1b991de52af7c554899f9f3e7","tid":642252,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"廢老必須死"},{"pid":"20f618acbbdc6b6a4df9b236841c77affadfceb2","tid":642252,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"膠鞋累男童被夾扶手梯　消防溫柔安 <br />\nGay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}